{"tid":1343052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推領事館] 外遊警告","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:32:57.000Z","uid":268559,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"222a01d38f70a9f13c67870bc3d396ef4673883c","tid":1343052,"uid":268559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:14:59.000Z","msg":"推出國際，一班居港中國人敵視外國勢力，隨街持械傷人，對各國僑民旅客帶來嚴重威脅，各國必須正視危險，保護自己國民，對香港發出最高級別外遊警告。<br />\n<br />\n外遊警告一經生效，保險公司將不承保，對香港經濟帶來沈重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n焦土格言<br />\n<br />\nIf we burn, you will burn with us."},{"pid":"cb6e584e0c657f871a5e62028789612a27cd80c1","tid":1343052,"uid":268559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"235c8787fa41438e2cf5272c466b32865274c13c","tid":1343052,"uid":115306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cf9ce74badaebc4cdb3811362af35ae15f8e9109","tid":1343052,"uid":268559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:22:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e5bb6b9d33d36f1de98687cdc8cf761a1c30914","tid":1343052,"uid":281977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:22:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0f5723a922badb21260bc55365d8dabc5c6890d","tid":1343052,"uid":268559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:32:02.000Z","msg":"呼籲持外國護照無中國籍港人，或使用外國護照入境香港(唔計BNO)港人，如在今日衝突中受傷，向所屬領事館求助，推動外國發出旅遊警告保護國民。"},{"pid":"d00810bc0350c90fc19360dda6981292448136a3","tid":1343052,"uid":262737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:32:57.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"}]}